---
title: Cheesy Bacon & Black Bean Enchiladas with Tomato Salsa
description: We decided to shake things up on the enchilada front by adding bacon to a black bean, capsicum and corn filling. The result? It did just what we hoped it would, giving a deliciously rich flavour that rounds them off perfectly.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d260dca1640ab000d37bb0d-19022415.jpg
